    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this function is considered medium. While scalar functions are straightforward, the complexity arises from the need to correctly determine the fiscal year based on specific business rules, which involve date manipulations and conditional logic."
