    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function's business logic involves determining the fiscal year based on the input date. The workflow includes:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Extracting the year from the input date."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Applying business rules to determine if the fiscal year should be the same as the calendar year or if it should be adjusted based on a fiscal year start date that differs from January 1st."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Returning the calculated fiscal year as an integer."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function involve conditional checks to determine if the input date falls before or after a specific cutoff date within the year, which would dictate whether the fiscal year is the current year or the next."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "6. Performance Considerations"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Scalar functions can have performance implications, especially when used in SELECT statements that process large datasets. Each invocation of the function can introduce overhead, as it is executed row-by-row. To mitigate performance issues:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Consider using inline table-valued functions if the logic can be expressed in a single query."
